title: Wash with vinegar prior to prime and paint to remove sheen and adhere primer.
review: Went to Sherwin-Williams to get the correct primer for these galvanized containers. Once primed I was able to paint. Make certain to wash with vinegar water to remove sheen from galvanized metal before priming. Sherwin-Williams will know which primer and paint to buy
